text:
QUIZ: Do You Know These Celebrities By Their Real Government Names? Will the real Amanda Lee Rogers please stand up?! by Damian Bellino 21h ago 
What’s in a name? A whole hell of a lot and when you want to see your names in light, you better make sure that name is one the plebs will remember. Some celebrities have such unusual names (ahem, Whoopi Goldberg , ya feel us?) but they are so ingrained in our pop culture brains, we never think twice about it being a stage name. 
How well do you know your favorite musicians and actors? Do you know what they were christened when they were but a wee one? Take our quiz now and thank us later. 
Love celebs? Gearing up for the Oscars? Catch up on our Oscar Conspiracies now so you’re in the know.
